{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928020/extras/steam_intro_cinematic_screen_anim1.gif?t=1734431368\" /><br><br><strong>NOW AVAILABLE FOR MAC!</strong><br><br>Take on the galaxy spanning Bloc in a run of tight, chunky twin-stick shooting. Only your weapons, a bunch of upgrades and your wits, will take you through the gauntlet of the Scunners Run.<br><br><strong>Chunky, physical combat</strong><br>Enemies and obstacles drift and collide, railguns beams reflect, EMP bursts disable shields and engines, weapons have secondary effects that can hurt you as much as the enemy. Discover the mini combat-sandbox and see how you can twist it for your own gain. <br><br><strong>Customise your run</strong><br>Fast, twitchy shooting against a variety of enemies that can kill you quickly. Go for more defensive upgrades if you struggle to stay alive, or load up on aggressive ones to let offence be your defence. <br><br><strong>See how far you can get</strong><br>The difficulty ramps up fast, so be prepared to die. See how far your run takes you. Did you unlock anything? Did you reach the boss...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928020/extras/steam_gameplay1.gif?t=1734431368\" /><br><br>Loosely based on the 2017 Glasgow Global Game Jam Winner &quot;Spacewaves 2079&quot;.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Budding Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2928020/59393c07836ccb1f9b431d4e37c8cbc4d9998b3c.jpg"},{"name":"Strapped","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2928020/b78590999c2af93a2ae11d4b90e52ff09fe5282c.jpg"},{"name":"Tinkerer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2928020/7c2321808a78f08b6c7d62975dfb8307dd20c2ab.jpg"},{"name":"Baby Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pub